{"tid":1880954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本從南到北有新增確診　世衛專家：全球最擔心日本","createTime":"2020-02-15T08:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T10:17:31.000Z","uid":224066,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"936779e52e080b1fc264c2fa4d910a9dff4b95bd","tid":1880954,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e476906a5af56141f1d38b3.jpg/Y66YqFWj_8f7VNlDwL5G7Q_hnoxrUlXHmEiROJhIkTg?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e476906a5af56141f1d38b3.jpg%2FY66YqFWj_8f7VNlDwL5G7Q_hnoxrUlXHmEiROJhIkTg%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=afe67d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗稱「武漢肺炎」的2019年冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫情持續，日本更有走向社區傳染的趨勢。該國單在2月14日一天就增加8宗確診個案，北到北海道、南到沖繩都有人「中招」，令人擔心日本會有「隱形爆發」（stealth outbreak）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e474518a5af56141f1d3898.jpg/dqnjBVcUAPyIVVB_ypw4DQGuPRs4L9xJw-YlLcPmJS0?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e474518a5af56141f1d3898.jpg%2FdqnjBVcUAPyIVVB_ypw4DQGuPRs4L9xJw-YlLcPmJS0%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=5691cbaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本共同網14日引述世界衛生組織（WHO）高級顧問進藤奈邦子當天表示：「在中國湖北省武漢市，確診的患者人數已出現減少趨勢，隧道盡頭看到亮光了。現在全球擔心的是日本。希望堅持努力。」<br />\n<br />\n日本厚生勞動省14日公布，當日東京、神奈川、和歌山、愛知縣、沖繩及北海道6個都道縣都有新個案，在和歌山出現第二名確診病人後，日本人國內有8人確診感染病毒。<br />\n<br />\n和歌山醫院第三宗確診 醫生疑受同事感染<br />\n<br />\n位於和歌山縣淺湯町的「濟生會有田醫院」迄今有3人確診。15日出現的第三名確診患者也是這間醫院的醫生。<br />\n<br />\n縣內第一名確診患者，是這間醫院一名50多歲的外科醫生確診，他在13日確診。第二名確診患者則是13日來到醫院就醫，之後入院，14日確診患上武漢肺炎。第三名確診患者，則是第一名確診患者的醫生同事。<br />\n<br />\n的士公會聚會 成為播毒場所<br />\n<br />\n東京有2人確診感染新型冠狀病毒，分別是50多歲的士車行女員工，以及春酒聚會場地屋型船的70多歲職員，他們均曾與一位2月13日確診感染的男的士司機密切接觸。春酒聚會有約80人參加，他們都是的士車行公會成員，約10人有發燒徵狀。<br />\n<br />\n愛知縣名古屋市有一名60多歲男子確診感染新型冠狀病毒，他2月3日在美國夏威夷渡假時已有感冒徵狀，回國後2日8日發燒至39度，2月14日確診。<br />\n<br />\n沖繩縣首例的65歲的士女司機，她2月1日曾開車接載當天停泊在那霸的郵輪「鑽石公主號」4名外國乘客，5日出現咳嗽徵狀，12日確診。她在1日至7日期間，曾接載過近50名乘客。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQjgWcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQjgWcR.jpg&h=3186f97c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n急救隊員運送郵輪病人「中招」<br />\n<br />\n北海道政府14日也宣布新增1名確診患者。當地第二宗確診個案為50多歲、沒有出國紀錄的男子。他1月31日自稱出現包括發燒的徵狀，2月4日被診斷為肺炎。他11日入院，14日確診感染。<br />\n<br />\n日本2月14日確認，在該國第3班、即1月31日從武漢飛返日本的撤僑包機中，有一宗確感染新型冠狀病毒個案。<br />\n<br />\n此外日本政府14日晚上公布，神奈川縣一名負責運送「鑽石公主號」郵輪患者的30多歲消防隊急救隊人感染新型冠狀病毒。他2月10日下午3時左右曾運送確診染病的郵輪患者到醫院，期間約40分鐘，男子有口罩及護目鏡，他同日晚上發燒，之後在2月14日確診。"},{"pid":"0c8ba3fc7e3f19ecd1f022c4b83076adf24899cd","tid":1880954,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"多難興邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92e28e2b2925f3de9ac9ca7023f68accc091119","tid":1880954,"uid":40276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"男子有口罩及護目鏡，他同日晚上發燒，之後在2月14日確診。<br />\n真係CLS<br />\n究竟點先傳播中招都未知"},{"pid":"67a5f8c374cf6e815c2949dd7e7081a2270e3bfc","tid":1880954,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=7de2854e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"d4bba1f9757119fa94dbfd499c0fec42df6c376b","tid":1880954,"uid":35600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻逼習"},{"pid":"bfd1ea96c8dbef95b9c3900db2ac1c2231294e19","tid":1880954,"uid":216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"世衛：支國唔屬於地球"},{"pid":"b55d4d683c5c709108be30fdb23aa7c747a14f3b","tid":1880954,"uid":343033,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cfd4cd0262a1d5ac0aa5d2dbb1deb1ba36310f9","tid":1880954,"uid":224882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"中國人死幾多都唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望日本可以大步檻過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fadd8c11f4dbc7b3a3789f0e13067dae4f07c3a","tid":1880954,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55d4d683c5c709108be30fdb23aa7c747a14f3b","tid":1880954,"uid":343033,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:01:18.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲有咩人會關心"},{"pid":"88bc1d72baa4aed09ee58db0c0027d5297d34ac9","tid":1880954,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"日本政府太信CHO 冇及時防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de061706e6eec80da41fecde86624d3e71f97823","tid":1880954,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"唔係可防可控咩？"},{"pid":"43a60293c394e691cb4ac144336f48c0340c09b0","tid":1880954,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"之前有一個患者<br />\n<br />\n迫過幾日JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50cc41dd6ebb483d4d8970882da0be977460e6b","tid":1880954,"uid":324649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cfd4cd0262a1d5ac0aa5d2dbb1deb1ba36310f9","tid":1880954,"uid":224882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20